English: We found their boss!
Welcome.

Japanese:
オレがハンターＪ。
ナイトシェイドのリーダーだ。
English: I'm Hunter J, Nightshade's Leader.

Japanese:
ここまで来るとは
見上げたもんだな。
English: It's admirable that you were able to make it this far.

Japanese:
その人形……
ガキのくせに、たいしたものを
持ってるじゃねぇか。
English:
That mech...
You're just brats, but it looks like you've got your hands on something good, hm?

Japanese:
だが、
マリオネーションギアはなぁ、
ガキの玩具じゃねぇんだよ。
English: However, Marionation Gear isn't a toy for kids to play with.

Japanese:
マリオネーションギアは力だ。
力を手に入れて、
ナイトシェイドは変わった。
English: Marionation Gear is power. With this power, Nightshade has transformed the world.

Japanese:
わかるか？
古臭いカラクリ人形の時代は
終わった。
English:
Do you get it?
The days of rusty old Karakuri Puppets are over.

Japanese:
今やマリオネーションギアは
世界のパワーバランスを変える
ほどの兵器となったのさ。
English: These weapons have tipped the power balance of the world.

Japanese:
お前らには
分不相応ってもんだよ。
English: And you don't have a place in it.

Japanese:
教えてやるぜ。
戦いの怖さってやつを。
人形使いを気取るガキどもにな。
English:
I'll tell you why. 
You're scared of fighting. You're just a kid pretending to be a Puppeteer.

Japanese:
お前の仲間も今頃、
なぶり殺しにされてるぜ。
English: Right about now, your friends are being slowly tormented until they die.
And, it's your turn next.

Japanese:
これ以上はいかせないよ。
ガロイ工房の人形使い。
English: I won't let you go any further, Puppeteer from the Galouye Workshop.
Hunter L!

Japanese:
ガキが調子に乗りすぎた
ようだね。
English: Looks like you brats have gotten a bit too carried away.

Japanese: なぶり殺しにしてやるよ。
English: I'm going to enjoy crushing you.

Japanese:
このおばさんは、
任せてもらおう。
English: Leave this grandma to me.
What did you just say?

Japanese:
このガキ！
楽には死なせないよ。
English: You brat! I won't let you die an easy death.

Japanese:
さんざんいたぶってから、
殺してやる！
English: I'm going to thoroughly torture you before I kill you!

Japanese:
何をしてる！
はやく行け！
English:
What are you doing?!
Hurry up and get out of here!
Ein!!
Go!
